The,City,of,Helsinki,provides,a,Geocoder,API,that,allows,users,to,access,geospatial,information,relevant,to,the,Helsinki,metropolitan,area,This,API,uses,REST,calls,issued,in,JSON,format,to,give,developers,access,to,its,functions,Currently,it,offers,functions,for,converting,from,addresses,to,coordinates,converting,from,coordinates,to,addresses,searching,for,points,of,interest,and,looking,up,city,plans,and,districts,A,demo,portal,is,provided,so,that,users,can,try,the,service,out,on,the,website